data.description: HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT, AND $15,000.00 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY DOWN!   Introducing this beautiful 4 bed, 3 bath, 2,472 SqFt of heated living space property with a den, and 3 car garage located in the gated community of Copperstone which offers a wide array of amenities. As you enter the home, you'll notice the stunning tile flooring throughout. The interior has been freshly painted. The versatile den space offers endless possibilities, allowing you to transform it to suit your lifestyle and needs. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, large cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a pantry closet, making it a chef's dream. The master bathroom impresses with a garden tub, walk-in shower with a glass enclosure, private water closet, and a huge walk-in closet. Bedroom 2 conveniently connects to a bathroom, which can also be accessed from the lanai, offering great convenience for guests. Bedrooms 3 and 4 share a bathroom, making it perfect for a growing family or hosting visitors. The yard is tranquil, with no neighbors behind, providing a peaceful ambiance. The covered and screened lanai is perfect for enjoying the outdoors year-round. The 3 car garage features epoxy flooring, ensuring a pristine look. The gated community offers multiple amenities, including a pool, clubhouse, fitness center, tennis/basketball court, and playground, allowing for an active and enjoyable lifestyle. This home is conveniently located close to many shopping, dining and entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your new home.
